sentence: This Information Statement has been filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission and is being furnished, pursuant to Section 14C of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended (the “ Exchange Act ”), to the holders (the “ Stockholders ”) of the common stock, par value $ .0001 per share (the “ Common Stock ”), of Comcam, Inc., a Delaware Corporation (the “ Company ”), to notify such Stockholders that on or about March 5, 2010, the Company received written consents in lieu of a meeting of Stockholders from holders of 683,952,500 shares representing approximately 91 % of the 744,640,134 shares of the total issued and outstanding shares of voting stock of the Company (the “ Majority Stockholders ”) to authorize 1-for-85 reverse stock split (pro-rata reduction of outstanding shares) of our issued and outstanding shares of Common Stock (the “ Reverse Stock Split ”).
